| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-1050 — Recovery Inhibition (fog)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 6f73dd49-75a7-5e2c-bfbf-c31321fdbd71"
